			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Menace letter from Branca Rodrigues, the wife of a merchant, to her parents, Diogo Rodrigues Chaves and Luísa Mendes.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author tells her parents that either that come forward and present themselves to the Inquisition or they won't have grounds to complaint about her (and, presumably) her testimony.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">Branca Rodrigues was accused of Judaism by the Inquisition of Coimbra while her husband, a merchant, was away. So she turned to her parents for help.</p>
				<p sameAs="text"></p></change>
		</revisionDesc>
